flowchart TD
  A[Trigger: Periodic data refresh and validation cycle.]
  A --> N1[Stream: DDM/Crawlers - Retrieve sales forecast data from SAP S/4HANA.]
  N1 --> N2[Stream: STREAMS - Validate and harmonize sales forecast data.]
  N2 --> N3[Stream: DDM/Crawlers - Retrieve production schedule data from SAP S/4HANA.]
  N3 --> N4[Stream: STREAMS - Validate production schedule data against inventory inputs.]
  N4 --> N5[Stream: DDM/Crawlers - Retrieve supplier lead times and capacities from SAP S/4HANA.]
  N5 --> N6[Stream: STREAMS - Update supplier lead times and capacities.]
  N6 --> N7[Stream: DDM/Crawlers - Retrieve dealer order backlog data from SAP S/4HANA.]
  N7 --> N8{Stream: STREAMS - Integrate dealer order backlog data into finished goods allocation.}
  N8 -->|Primary| P1[Action: Autonomous validation and alignment of inputs, triggering end-to-end decisions.]
  P1 --> Z1[Outcome: Reduced working capital, lower COGS, improved on-time delivery, and optimized order fulfillment.]
  N8 -->|Inaccurate sales forecast data detected.| B1[Trigger data correction workflow.]
  B1 --> O1[Outcome: Corrected sales forecast data used for subsequent steps.]
  O1 --> End[End]
  N8 -->|Production schedule data does not ali...| B2[Adjust production schedule data.]
  B2 --> O2[Outcome: Aligned production schedule data used for subsequent steps.]
  O2 --> End[End]
  N8 -->|Supplier lead times or capacities are...| B3[Update supplier lead times and capacities.]
  B3 --> O3[Outcome: Updated supplier data used for subsequent steps.]
  O3 --> End[End]
  Z1 --> End[End]